    Scenario: Convert a template from a draft to a Template
    When I elect to login as "mediaProducer1" user
    Then I elect to edit the course named "course1.templatename"
    Then I elect to update the value of the course to the the following values
    |courseStatus   | activeOnDate   | saveBtn |
